Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:52.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:00.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Withdraw at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the Simoun among the Argentine forces today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:27.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a show of force, to prove to us that they can attack whenever they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that really is what they're capable of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:42.57,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Eternal Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's really over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:49.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we can finally live a life... of simply performing prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:56.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:58.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does everything feel so bleah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see that other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that grandpa was always yearning for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,The world different from this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I became a sibylla so I could go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then, Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:49.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that it's possible that Amuria is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's rather inconsiderate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:06.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mr. Vice-Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, do not call me by that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer hold that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:21.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if it falls and its life has ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,it can at least comfort someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you attend the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,"It can at least comfort someone," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't even do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can no longer protect Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:55.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:05.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two conditions are the terms that the Archipelago and the Highlands set for their peace treaty. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was never informed of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:11.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Superficially, at least, we are to be treated as their equals. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,And who should take the credit for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would like for you to think long and hard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,"War is utter foolishness."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military governors from Plumbum and Argentum have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, for now—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really the way things should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:07:00.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the girls' prayers to continue in the peaceful skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that was all I wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with this decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way the High Priestess was acting just now... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are they still here, even though the peace ceremony is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard that some of their forces will be staying here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm starting to not understand what this "peace" is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until they found the ancient Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}their{\i0} comrades were the ones who were dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is what their faces look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:55.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,All those faces that we blotted out with our Ri Maajons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we didn't even know what they looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,They probably didn't know either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the food's getting cold. Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Rodoreamon, won't you have some fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've been getting too thin lately! You need some nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura, it's like you're her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, your feet are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Move those filthy legs outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not that you guys can understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? You at least get that I'm yelling at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have committed a terrible sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're taking a shower, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, lend me your soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yours are... pretty big, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:44.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Th-They just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. Because you're going to become a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless I become a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless I become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I cannot protect what's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, Neviril told me something once...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,To get stronger through someone else's embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not the right way, Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:21.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only when both of you are strong can you really embrace each other. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:31.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I also thought I wanted to be a man, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I can pull it off right now, without having to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you accept yourself, life will be much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you stayed at the Ruins, so how...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you thought that to be true, then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place is extremely unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins were the training ground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:53.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Many incomplete Emerald Ri Maajons collapsed and exploded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Helical Motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,They are said to manipulate time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because of that, space-time was distorted,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:09.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,and that caused the Spring to exist simultaneously in two different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are not many things that people can believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:25.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...when they cannot even believe in themselves. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}was{\i0} struggling to stay close to my fallen comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:43.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I was trying to escape to a place far away from their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,How... how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I am the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I avoided ever making my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried to escape to a place far away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:04.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe... that I've been waiting for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:10.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,For someone to listen to me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,To hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,...my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,As one of the terms of our peace treaty with Plumbum and Argentum,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will be disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is Yun at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:53.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest, disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we worked so hard all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:07.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the Plumbish priestesses will be taking over our duties, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. Is this what peace is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perfect equality is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:17.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,We know one thing for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The simple truth is that we are no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:38.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And just when we were finally able to understand the true meaning of our prayers as sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if Chor Tempest ceases to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it does not change the fact that we are Simoun sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one will ever defile our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Chor Tempest is disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Whaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we will no longer be able to fly the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to the other world... will be closed to us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've always longed to see that other world, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:42.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we last talked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:12.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:13.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you bless me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up? Are you sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:50.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you asking me about Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bull's-eye, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,She talks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could always just shut her up with your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, it's always about kissing with you, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before you were telling me about wanting to kiss someone when you like them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you wanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:22.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not the way Neviril is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,What, you don't like her anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmpf! You're just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...? I feel so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! What do you mean, "serious?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not just Neviril, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you've changed too, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:46.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:12.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is Sibylla Aaeru? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it, Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:20.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta, you'll do. Please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me, please, hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must fly, Sibylla Paraietta, Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:41.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no time to spare! We must hurry! We must hurry or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door will close on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it will never open again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The door?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was a member of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamt of the Emerald Ri Maajon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:04.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamt of becoming an Eternal Maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Eternal Maiden?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun is like a maiden herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maiden... wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:18.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun Gem reflects that wavering heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maiden... drifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:25.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forever escaping from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:32.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,she paints the sky... with her unending beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:52.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please slow down, Your Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:57.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}must{\i0} change our country's fortunes! We cannot go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,If things continue like this, we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quickly! You must fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the land of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:39.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is there something that you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:46.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... want to hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:51.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,As your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you run away from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,and refuse to decide on your sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,these are the consequences.
